snippet.title: Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League Official Story Trailer – “Ticking”
snippet.description:
Welcome to Task Force X. Your mission? Kill the Justice League.

Watch the official #StoryTrailer of #SuicideSquadGame in #4K.

Coming in 2022 to PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC.

Learn more: https://www.suicidesquadgame.com/
